{"tid":1658172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【屍政報告】林鄭會唔會只係轉移視線？","createTime":"2019-10-16T12:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T12:18:41.000Z","uid":237209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc24cd8138e649ac0d8439f520d67327a266421","tid":1658172,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"個個都將成份嘢嘅重點集中喺900萬上車個位<br />\n其實我覺得有樣嘢仲大陰謀<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「已預留10億元為600多所資助學校進行小型內部改裝」</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n點解要無端端撥呢筆錢做啲「小型內部改裝」？<br />\n所謂改裝又係咩意思？<br />\n每間學校平均嚟計都分到160萬<br />\n斷估都唔係幫學校更換黑板添置文具呢類嘢<br />\n亦冇必要將呢種小事寫落施政報告焦點<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係安裝一啲<span style=\"color: red;\">類似新疆嘅監察系統</span>呢？<br />\n美其名係提升學習效率<br />\n其實就想搬大陸嗰套落嚟<br />\n方便遲啲做洗腦工作<br />\n同埋禁止校園抗爭活動<br />\n從而打擊學生參與社運<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"4940e86c127e8d19e7c2734c133b2dd09393bad2","tid":1658172,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a477c1a3416954230b958da6ce269b7d14d5b165","tid":1658172,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:11:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fa54eec497ad0d19727f46a8b2fcbe01f8d9895","tid":1658172,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c8f36aa860e4f1380efb3377cb5f40d091653c6","tid":1658172,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:12:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e22e977b2681cbd5bc8993d9cbc6de79ae976007","tid":1658172,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"似啦"}]}